      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne ¶ 28 Aug. 1884. ¶ The honorable  ¶  ¶ Graham Berry M.L.A., ¶ Chief Secretary. ¶ Sir...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">84.08.28</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Graham Berry</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">B84/7688, unit 60, VPRS 3992/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">28 Aug. 1884.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">The honorable <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Graham Berry M.L.A.,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Chief Secretary.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor to solicit, that you will be pleased to allow me to proceed for a few weeks to the N. W. part of Victoria,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Berry approved M's proposition on 2 September and the Under Secretary, T. Wilson, immediately sent the file to M.</p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See also M to T. Wilson, 15 September 1884, announcing his departure, and M to G. Berry, 28 September 1884, where M informs Berry of his return from the trip. The file also contains a minute to M<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>from Wilson,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>dated<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>24 October, that he had not returned the file containing the letter [B7688] above. M apologised and returned the file the next day: 'By some oversight, which I regret, the document 7688 was retained at my office.'</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>where I wish for the completion of the records on the Victorian Flora to examine the spring-vegetation. The country between Lake Hindmarsh and the South Australian Boundary I have never yet examined in reference to its vegetation, it being not or but little accessible when I explored formerly. I shall, if you kindly approve of my proposition, remain in daily communication with my Department. While completing thus a portion of the labours on the Victorian Flora, I hope also to subdue more fully my pulmonary sufferings, while enjoying the mild vernal air of the N.W.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I beg to avail myself of this opportunity, honorable Sir, to thank you for the permission accorded me, to do my Office-work during the winter months at Dr Buettners<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Alexander<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Büttner.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>healthy place of residence, whereby my recovery was much promoted.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Sir, your obedient servant</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</seg>
            </p>
         </div>
